dct_description_sm: Iraq. Mudiriyat Amur al-Misaha. Iraq. Directorate of Surveying Affairs. [[Map of Iraq]: ash-Sharqat section.] Alternate title: Liwa' al-Mawsil: qada' al-Mausil: nahiyat ash-Sharqat. [Mosul province: Mosul district: ash-Sharqat section.] Relief shown by hachure, form lines, and contour lines at 1 meter intervals. Heights are shown with spot heights. Triangulation points are shown. Surveyed: 1937-38. Tribal lands and land ownership are shown. 1935
